 Season Awards 2012/13|date=29 April 2013|publisher=Walsall FC|accessdate=13 July 2019}}</ref>\n* [[2013\u201314 Walsall F.C. season|2013\u201314]] {{flagicon|England}} [[Sam Mantom]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://footballleagueworld.co.uk/walsall-boss-says-mantoms-not-for-sale123/|title=Walsall boss says Mantom's not for sale|date=17 July 2014|publisher=Football League World|accessdate=13 July 2019}}</ref>\n* [[2014\u201315 Walsall F.C. season|2014\u201315]] {{flagicon|England}} [[Richard O'Donnell]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.expressandstar.com/sport/football/walsall-fc/2015/05/04/goalkeeper-richard-odonnell-named-walsalls-player-of-the-season/|title=O'Donnell is Walsall's Player of the Season|date=4 May 2015|publisher=Express & Star|accessdate=13 July 2019}}</ref>\n* [[2015\u201316 Walsall F.C. season|2015\u201316]] {{flagicon|England}} [[Adam Chambers]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36249546|title=Walsall captain signs new one-year contract with promotion hopefuls|date=9 May 2016|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=13 July 2019}}</ref>\n* [[2016\u201317 Walsall F.C. season|2016\u201317]] {{flagicon|England}} [[Jason McCarthy]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.expressandstar.com/sport/football/walsall-fc/2017/05/02/walsall-stars-receive-their-awards/|title=Walsall stars receive their awards|date=2 May 2017|publisher=Express & Star|accessdate=13 July 2019}}</ref>\n* [[2017\u201318 Walsall F.C. season|2017\u201318]] {{flagicon|England}} [[Joe Edwards (footballer, born 1990)|Joe Edwards]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.saddlers.co.uk/news/2018/may/201718-awards/|title=2017/18 Awards Recap|date=6 May 2018|publisher=Walsall FC|accessdate=13 July 2019}}</ref>\n* [[2018\u201319 Walsall F.C. season|2018\u201319]] {{flagicon|England}} [[Andy Cook (footballer, born 1990)|Andy Cook]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.saddlers.co.uk/news/2019/may/cook-named-201819-player-of-the-season/|title=Cook named 2018/19 Player of the Season!|date=4 May 2019|publ