ootball League Trophy Final|2015]]</small>\n|align=left|\n|-\n|}\n\n==Honours and achievements==\n\n===League===\n\n'''[[Football League Third Division]] / [[EFL League One|League One]]''' (3rd tier)\n*Runners-up ('''2'''): [[1960\u201361 in English football|1960\u201361]], [[1998\u201399 in English football|1998\u201399]]\n*Play-off winners ('''2'''): [[1988 Football League Third Division play-off Final|1987\u201388]], [[2001 Football League Second Division play-off Final|2000\u201301]]\n\n'''[[Football League Fourth Division]] / [[EFL League Two|League Two]]''' (4th tier)\n*Champions ('''2'''): [[1959\u201360 in English football|1959\u201360]], [[2006\u201307 in English football|2006\u201307]]\n*Runners-up ('''2'''): [[1979\u201380 in English football|1979\u201380]], [[1994\u201395 in English football|1994\u201395]]\n\n===Cup===\n\n'''[[EFL Trophy|Football League Trophy]]'''\n*Runners-up ('''1'''): [[2015 Football League Trophy Final|2015]]\n\n'''[[Football League Third Division North Cup|Third Division North Cup]]'''\n*Runners-up ('''1'''): [[1934\u201335 in English football|1935]]\n\n'''[[Football League Third Division South Cup|Third Division South Cup]]'''\n*Runners-up ('''1'''): [[1945\u201346 in English football|1946]]\n\n'''[[Birmingham Senior Cup]]'''\n*Winners ('''3'''): 1896\u201397, 1897\u201398, 1993\u201394\n*Runners-up ('''3'''): 1907\u201308, 1999\u201300, 2006\u201307\n\n'''[[Staffordshire Senior Cup]]'''\n*Winners ('''4'''): 1922\u201323, 1926\u201327, 1928\u201329, 1967\u201368\n*Runners-up ('''12'''): 1889\u201390, 1892\u201393, 1898\u201399, 1910\u201311, 1913\u201314, 1920\u201321, 1921\u201322, 1930\u201331, 1948\u201349, 1949\u201350, 1952\u201353, 1965\u201366\n\n'''[[Walsall Senior Cup]]'''\n*Winners ('''3'''): 1888\u201389, 2014\u201315, 2016\u201317\n*Runners-up ('''1'''): 2012\u201313\n\n==Club records==\n\n'''Competitions'''\n\n* Highest ever [[Football League]] position: '''6th''', [[Football League Second Division|Second Division]] [